				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">512KB PRG (Battle Kid 2), self flashable (not yet used), and 4x 8KB CHR RAM banks (Assimilate) are very cheap additions to UNROM.  Like the 8T-ROM using flash instead of battery backed WRAM removes much of the need for MMC1/MMC3.  The CHR banking makes background animations usually done with CHR ROM easy.  Still no IRQ but $5-10 cheaper per cart.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

